<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.8">
<l>tuvaritta vuṭaiyārkkun tūymaiyillāc camaṇarkkum</l>
<l>avarkaṭkaṅ karuḷillā varuḷāṉai taṉṉaṭainta</l>
<l>vemarkaṭku maṭiyēṟku memmāṟku memmaṉaikkum</l>
<l>amararkkum pirāṉāraik kaṇṭatuteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] beholding of the one who is mercy [but] without mercy</l>
<l rend="indent">toward the saffron robed [Buddhists] or the unclean Jains,</l>
<l>The one who is the lord to his people who take refuge in him,</l>
<l>To me, his devotee, to my father, to my mother,</l>
<l>And to the immortals, was in Araṅkam of the South.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
